{"word":"G1304 - διατρίβω - diatríbō - dee-at-ree'-bo - Abide","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διατρίβω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diatríbō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-at-ree'-bo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Abide</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சஞ்சரி, தங்கியிரு, வாசம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to rub between, rub hard, to wear away, consume; to spend, pass time, simply to stay, tarry"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5147 - τρίβος - tríbos - tree'-bos/5147\">G5147</a>; to <i>wear through</i> (time), that is, <i>remain:</i> - abide, be, continue, tarry.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}